<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="CSS/style.css">
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <style>
        .custom-paragraph {
            text-align: justify;
            margin: 25px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #333;
        }

        .social-icon {
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 24px;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 5px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: transform 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;
            color: white;
        }

        .fa-facebook {
            background: #3B5998;
        }

        .fa-twitter {
            background: #55ACEE;
        }

        .fa-instagram {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #fdf497, #fd5949, #d6249f, #285AEB);
        }

        .social-icon:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .custom_container {
            position: relative;
            width: calc(100% - 40px);
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding-top: 100%;
            padding-left: 20px;
            padding-right: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .custom_responsive-iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>

    <p class="custom-paragraph">
        Welcome to the contact page of Mugged! We specialize in a wide range of personalized gifts tailored to your needs. Whether you have questions about our custom products, the ordering process, or need assistance in selecting the perfect gift, feel free to reach out. We look forward to helping you create memorable moments with our unique offerings!
    </p>

    <p class="custom-paragraph">
        For inquiries, you can reach us at:<br>
        Phone: <a href="tel:0726117505">0726117505</a> or <a href="tel:0726585833">0726585833</a>
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/muggedbycourts" class="fa fa-facebook social-icon" target="_blank"></a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/muggedbycourteney/" class="fa fa-instagram social-icon" target="_blank"></a>
    </div>

    <br>

    <div class="custom_container">
        <iframe class="custom_responsive-iframe"
